No, what kind of crappy computer is this?

00:31:24.680 --> 00:31:25.640
This is way too slow,

00:31:25.640 --> 00:31:26.900
it will never catch up.

00:31:27.280 --> 00:31:28.680
The computing load is too heavy.

00:31:28.680 --> 00:31:29.360
What a pity.

00:31:41.760 --> 00:31:44.680
Chao, Jia, Yan.

00:31:45.840 --> 00:31:47.170
Thank you all for today.

00:31:47.280 --> 00:31:49.280
We will handle the rest ourselves.

00:31:52.760 --> 00:31:53.640
If there's any news,

00:31:53.640 --> 00:31:55.700
I will notify everyone immediately.

00:32:18.400 --> 00:32:19.040
Qin,

00:32:19.560 --> 00:32:21.220
how is the competition going?

00:32:21.280 --> 00:32:21.920
I managed to squeeze out

00:32:21.920 --> 00:32:23.980
three hours of machine time for them.

00:32:24.520 --> 00:32:26.080
Three, three hours?

00:32:26.080 --> 00:32:27.610
Are three hours not enough?

00:32:28.120 --> 00:32:30.850
Let me tell you, I'm working myself to death here.

00:32:31.440 --> 00:32:32.160
Enough, enough,

00:32:32.160 --> 00:32:33.720
it's enough.

00:32:35.560 --> 00:32:36.320
It's enough.

00:32:36.560 --> 00:32:37.840
Alright, that's it.

00:32:44.400 --> 00:32:45.040
Mr. Qin.

00:32:45.200 --> 00:32:46.720
What's the situation on your end?

00:32:46.720 --> 00:32:47.520
The software is finished,

00:32:47.520 --> 00:32:49.280
but we don't have enough time for data optimization.

00:32:49.280 --> 00:32:49.920
Right now,

00:32:49.920 --> 00:32:51.640
bring everything and come downstairs immediately.

00:32:51.640 --> 00:32:52.320
Now?

00:32:52.680 --> 00:32:54.810
I got you three hours of computer time.

00:32:55.200 --> 00:32:55.960
Is that enough?

00:32:55.960 --> 00:32:56.560
Enough.

00:32:56.720 --> 00:32:57.680
It's enough.

00:32:57.800 --> 00:32:59.840
Let's go.

00:33:00.640 --> 00:33:01.700
We have a computer.

00:33:09.720 --> 00:33:10.600
Hurry.

00:33:11.400 --> 00:33:11.760
Quick.

00:33:11.760 --> 00:33:12.720
Stop shaking.

00:33:28.920 --> 00:33:30.080
Go, Wei!

00:33:31.200 --> 00:33:32.930
Shut up, my legs are killing me.

00:33:33.360 --> 00:33:34.220
I can't hold on.

00:33:35.720 --> 00:33:36.640
I can't anymore.

00:33:36.640 --> 00:33:37.160
I can't.

00:33:41.000 --> 00:33:41.600
Caibao,

00:33:42.240 --> 00:33:42.640
hurry.

00:33:43.600 --> 00:33:44.240
Nan.

00:33:47.240 --> 00:33:47.970
I'll charge!

00:33:49.840 --> 00:33:51.160
My useless legs!

00:33:51.680 --> 00:33:52.320
It's fine.

00:33:57.320 --> 00:33:58.600
Hurry! Hurry!

00:34:17.639 --> 00:34:18.440
Charge!

00:35:01.440 --> 00:35:03.080
Mr. Gu, the hard drive.

00:35:03.680 --> 00:35:04.680
What's the panic?

00:35:05.360 --> 00:35:06.640
The more critical the moment is,

00:35:06.640 --> 00:35:08.900
the more you need to keep your composure.

00:35:14.520 --> 00:35:15.050
How is it?

00:35:50.200 --> 00:35:50.960
No way.

00:35:51.320 --> 00:35:53.200
The World Aerospace Association uploaded a new plan.

00:35:53.200 --> 00:35:55.160
It's ahead of the second place by over 2,000 points.

00:35:55.160 --> 00:35:56.360
Over 2,000 points?

00:35:56.360 --> 00:35:57.280
What the heck?

00:35:59.160 --> 00:35:59.920
Oh my god.

00:36:02.080 --> 00:36:03.200
What do we do now?

00:36:06.840 --> 00:36:07.920
The entire calculation process

00:36:07.920 --> 00:36:10.040
takes an hour and 40 minutes.

00:36:10.880 --> 00:36:12.080
Worrying won't help.

00:36:12.840 --> 00:36:13.800
How about this?

00:36:14.040 --> 00:36:14.840
We take turns.

00:36:15.000 --> 00:36:18.000
You guys go rest first. I'll keep an eye on things here.

00:36:18.360 --> 00:36:18.800
Okay.

00:36:20.200 --> 00:36:20.720
Mr. Gu.

00:36:22.280 --> 00:36:22.880
All right.

00:36:23.520 --> 00:36:24.980
I'll leave it to you, Ziqi.

00:36:25.120 --> 00:36:25.720
Go ahead.

00:36:25.720 --> 00:36:27.180
Thanks for your hard work.

00:36:27.360 --> 00:36:28.820
Let's go. We'll head back.

00:36:29.000 --> 00:36:29.860
I'm exhausted.

00:36:30.080 --> 00:36:31.610
This BMW is too hard to ride.

00:36:44.400 --> 00:36:45.440
Mr. Gu, Mr. Gu.

00:36:45.720 --> 00:36:48.320
Thank you so much for today.

00:36:48.960 --> 00:36:49.760
It's nothing.

00:36:52.480 --> 00:36:54.760
Lao Qin really knows his stuff.

00:36:54.760 --> 00:36:55.960
Thank you so much too.

00:36:56.280 --> 00:36:58.240
Show some respect and get your arm off me.

00:36:58.240 --> 00:36:59.120
Mind my image.

00:36:59.760 --> 00:37:00.760
What image?

00:37:01.240 --> 00:37:02.100
Let me tell you.

00:37:02.680 --> 00:37:04.480
About all of Mr. Qin's little secrets,

00:37:04.480 --> 00:37:05.740
I know them inside out.

00:37:05.840 --> 00:37:06.760
Tell me more.

00:37:06.880 --> 00:37:07.360
Really.

00:37:07.360 --> 00:37:08.080
Very funny.

00:37:09.680 --> 00:37:10.440
He's shy.

00:37:10.840 --> 00:37:11.880
If you want to maintain your image,

00:37:11.880 --> 00:37:13.160
you need to pay me some hush money.

00:37:13.160 --> 00:37:14.120
No, no money.

00:37:14.160 --> 00:37:15.680
I have no money, but you can take my life.

00:37:15.680 --> 00:37:16.720
Come on.

00:37:23.760 --> 00:37:24.480
Get up.

00:37:24.800 --> 00:37:25.560
We won.

00:37:25.760 --> 00:37:26.480
We won.

00:37:27.480 --> 00:37:28.240
Say it again.

00:37:30.120 --> 00:37:32.320
We are the champions. We are number one.

00:37:32.440 --> 00:37:33.800
What are you eating?

00:37:33.880 --> 00:37:35.040
Let's go to a restaurant.

00:37:35.040 --> 00:37:36.120
It's my treat.

00:37:36.240 --> 00:37:36.800
Do you know

00:37:36.800 --> 00:37:38.320
how many points we beat the foreign team by?

00:37:38.320 --> 00:37:39.760
Over 1,000 points.

00:37:40.000 --> 00:37:41.200
We finally won the championship.

00:37:41.200 --> 00:37:43.400
It's both interesting and meaningful.

00:37:45.600 --> 00:37:47.000
We won.

00:37:52.360 --> 00:37:53.420
Congratulations.

00:37:53.720 --> 00:37:55.380
Here, have some steamed buns.

00:37:55.800 --> 00:37:57.600
Every time we successfully complete a mission,

00:37:57.600 --> 00:37:58.730
we eat steamed buns.

00:37:59.200 --> 00:38:00.200
Now you know.

00:38:00.560 --> 00:38:02.420
This is our aerospace tradition.

00:38:02.640 --> 00:38:05.100
Without your seniors, you wouldn't be here.

00:38:05.280 --> 00:38:06.080
Yes, yes, yes.

00:38:06.120 --> 00:38:07.920
We sincerely thank our seniors.

00:38:08.840 --> 00:38:09.840
All right, eat up,

00:38:11.720 --> 00:38:13.000
little champions.

00:38:13.000 --> 00:38:14.160
Congratulations.

00:38:14.160 --> 00:38:15.560
Thank you, Director Cao.

00:38:15.640 --> 00:38:17.280
I came here specifically to tell you guys.

00:38:17.280 --> 00:38:18.880
Hurry up and get ready.

00:38:18.880 --> 00:38:20.740
There's an award ceremony later.

00:38:21.560 --> 00:38:23.760
We have to go abroad to receive the award.

00:38:23.760 --> 00:38:25.240
Do I have a suit? Do you have one?

00:38:25.240 --> 00:38:26.360
Why do you care if I have a suit or not?

00:38:26.360 --> 00:38:26.920
I have one, I have one.

00:38:26.920 --> 00:38:27.800
I, I have one.

00:38:28.560 --> 00:38:29.800
Going abroad?

00:38:30.000 --> 00:38:31.400
You're overthinking it.

00:38:31.560 --> 00:38:32.440
Receive the award online.

00:38:32.440 --> 00:38:33.840
Remember to take a video for me later.

00:38:33.840 --> 00:38:34.680
Don't forget.

00:38:34.840 --> 00:38:36.600
Receive the award online.

00:38:42.880 --> 00:38:43.480
Let's eat.

00:38:43.480 --> 00:38:44.280
Aren't there steamed buns?

00:38:44.280 --> 00:38:45.720
No more herbal jelly. Eat the buns.

00:38:45.720 --> 00:38:47.080
Eat the buns.

00:38:47.080 --> 00:38:47.880
Come on.

00:38:50.400 --> 00:38:52.200
One bite for you, one bite for me.

00:38:52.800 --> 00:38:53.600
They won.

00:38:54.400 --> 00:38:56.260
It's not like you got first place.

00:38:59.640 --> 00:39:03.120
The topic of this competition is 'Immigrating to the Milky Way'.

00:39:03.120 --> 00:39:04.480
In the vast universe,

00:39:04.640 --> 00:39:06.700
as intelligent life on a tiny planet,

00:39:07.360 --> 00:39:09.960
Human exploration of space has never stopped.

00:39:10.320 --> 00:39:11.080
We believe

00:39:11.080 --> 00:39:13.440
that at distances measured in light-years,

00:39:13.440 --> 00:39:15.920
we can see a brighter future.

00:39:16.520 --> 00:39:18.320
Earth is the cradle of humanity,

00:39:18.480 --> 00:39:19.280
but humanity

00:39:19.280 --> 00:39:21.210
cannot live in the cradle forever.

00:39:22.440 --> 00:39:24.800
This interesting and challenging topic

00:39:25.080 --> 00:39:25.840
allowed us to try to

00:39:25.840 --> 00:39:28.040
advance theories and methods,

00:39:28.160 --> 00:39:30.280
and enjoy the process of the competition.

00:39:30.280 --> 00:39:33.320
It not only expanded the dimensions of technology and knowledge,

00:39:33.320 --> 00:39:34.240
but also made us firmly believe

00:39:34.240 --> 00:39:36.200
that the cause we are engaged in

00:39:36.280 --> 00:39:39.410
is laying the foundation for the future of all humanity.

00:39:39.440 --> 00:39:40.760
Thanks to the organizing committee,

00:39:40.760 --> 00:39:42.620
and thanks to those who helped us.

00:39:42.680 --> 00:39:44.160
To win this championship

00:39:44.240 --> 00:39:45.520
is a great honor for us.

00:39:48.080 --> 00:39:50.140
But the people I want to thank the most

00:39:51.200 --> 00:39:52.320
are my teammates.

00:39:53.880 --> 00:39:56.000
Being able to complete this competition

00:39:56.000 --> 00:39:57.880
is precisely because we worked together,

00:39:57.880 --> 00:39:59.010
fought side by side,

00:39:59.400 --> 00:40:01.130
to overcome the difficulties.

00:40:02.040 --> 00:40:03.300
The beauty of humanity

00:40:03.560 --> 00:40:05.160
is not only in distant space,

00:40:05.520 --> 00:40:06.920
but also right beside us.

00:40:07.920 --> 00:40:08.680
In Guolai.

00:40:09.720 --> 00:40:12.120
No matter where humanity eventually goes,

00:40:12.560 --> 00:40:13.960
the most important thing

00:40:14.400 --> 00:40:16.400
will always be the people around us.

00:40:27.560 --> 00:40:28.600
Take a picture.

00:40:36.840 --> 00:40:39.600
One, two, three.

00:40:47.720 --> 00:40:49.440
Qi, are you okay?

00:40:51.600 --> 00:40:53.120
Don't help me up.

00:40:54.320 --> 00:40:55.360
No one help me.

00:40:55.360 --> 00:40:56.400
Don't touch me.

00:40:57.160 --> 00:40:58.490
Walk in a straight line.

00:41:00.680 --> 00:41:02.720
Hold him. What if he really falls?

00:41:02.720 --> 00:41:04.320
He said no one should help him.

00:41:04.320 --> 00:41:04.840
Right?

00:41:11.920 --> 00:41:12.560
Nan.

00:41:14.440 --> 00:41:16.160
You are really outstanding.

00:41:16.840 --> 00:41:17.720
Awesome.

00:41:18.400 --> 00:41:19.760
Be confident.

00:41:20.520 --> 00:41:22.050
I know it's not easy for you.

00:41:22.200 --> 00:41:23.080
You know?

00:41:23.280 --> 00:41:24.280
Ying Ziqi,

00:41:24.440 --> 00:41:26.680
watch your behavior in broad daylight.

00:41:27.320 --> 00:41:28.040
Keep it up.

00:41:32.560 --> 00:41:33.440
And you guys,

00:41:34.480 --> 00:41:35.240
listen to me.

00:41:38.880 --> 00:41:40.320
We are Team Muxing.

00:41:41.320 --> 00:41:43.000
Invincible.

00:41:43.560 --> 00:41:45.820
The future of the flight control center,

00:41:46.280 --> 00:41:48.320
it all depends on us.

00:41:48.760 --> 00:41:49.520
Okay.

00:41:53.120 --> 00:41:53.800
Ying Ziqi,

00:41:53.800 --> 00:41:54.600
turn around.

00:42:11.200 --> 00:42:12.600
What are you laughing at?

00:42:13.240 --> 00:42:15.640
It's championship night, can't I be happy?

00:42:17.120 --> 00:42:18.520
The competition is over.

00:42:19.640 --> 00:42:21.700
What's the plan for Team Muxing next?

00:42:23.720 --> 00:42:25.200
What are your plans?

00:42:26.160 --> 00:42:27.880
You and Nan...

00:42:34.720 --> 00:42:35.760
I won't tease you anymore.

00:42:35.760 --> 00:42:36.520
Seriously,

00:42:37.000 --> 00:42:38.120
I'm not bragging,

00:42:38.840 --> 00:42:39.400
I really think

00:42:39.400 --> 00:42:41.400
our little team has a bright future.

00:42:42.200 --> 00:42:44.440
Becoming full-time employees goes without saying.

00:42:44.440 --> 00:42:46.700
For the upcoming Hao 4 and Hao 5 missions,

00:42:47.080 --> 00:42:48.480
we can't be absent.

00:42:50.480 --> 00:42:51.810
Lunar far side landing,

00:42:52.040 --> 00:42:53.370
retrieving lunar soil,

00:42:53.640 --> 00:42:54.900
we can't miss any of it.

